<p class="MsoNormal">I believe the issue is actually in opal/util/malloc.h, Howard. I noticed this while looking around this weekend - someone included opal_config.h in the malloc.h file even though it explicitly says &quot;DON'T DO THIS&quot; &nbsp;in that header file.<o:p></o:p></p>
<div>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
